---
layout: base.njk
title: Shared Values
description: The beliefs that unite House Rabbit Society and Rabbit.org Foundation, drawn from their published philosophy pages and presented side by side.
---

<section class="page-hero">
  <h1>Shared Values</h1>
  <p>The beliefs that unite House Rabbit Society and Rabbit.org Foundation, drawn directly from their published philosophy pages.</p>
</section>

<div class="prose">
  <p>{{ directory.shared_values.intro }}</p>

  <div class="disclaimer">
    <strong>Disclaimer:</strong> Rabbit.org Foundation is an independent organization with no formal affiliation with House Rabbit Society. This page presents their published values side by side for educational purposes only.
  </div>

  <div class="values-grid">
    {%- for value in directory.shared_values.values %}
    <div class="value-card">
      <div class="value-card-header">
        <div class="value-card-topline">
          <span class="value-emoji">{{ value.emoji }}</span>
          {%- if value.source == "both" %}
          <span class="value-source-tag tag-both">Both</span>
          {%- elif value.source == "hrs" %}
          <span class="value-source-tag tag-hrs">HRS</span>
          {%- elif value.source == "rorg" %}
          <span class="value-source-tag tag-rorg">Rabbit.org</span>
          {%- endif %}
        </div>
        <h3 class="value-statement" id="{{ value.statement | slugify }}">{{ value.statement }}</h3>
      </div>
      <div class="value-quotes">
        <div class="value-quote{% if not value.hrs_quote %} value-quote-empty{% endif %}">
          <span class="value-quote-label">House Rabbit Society</span>
          {%- if value.hrs_quote %}
          "{{ value.hrs_quote }}"
          {%- else %}
          <span class="value-quote-none">No specific language</span>
          {%- endif %}
        </div>
        <div class="value-quote{% if not value.rorg_quote %} value-quote-empty{% endif %}">
          <span class="value-quote-label">Rabbit.org Foundation</span>
          {%- if value.rorg_quote %}
          "{{ value.rorg_quote }}"
          {%- else %}
          <span class="value-quote-none">No specific language</span>
          {%- endif %}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    {%- endfor %}
  </div>

  <h2>Read More</h2>
  <div class="resource-links">
    <a class="resource-link" href="{{ directory.shared_values.sources.hrs.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <strong>House Rabbit Society</strong>
      <span>Mission and philosophy: houserabbit.org</span>
    </a>
    <a class="resource-link" href="{{ directory.shared_values.sources.rorg.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
      <strong>Rabbit.org Foundation</strong>
      <span>Philosophy: rabbit.org</span>
    </a>
  </div>

  <p>We encourage you to read both organizations' full philosophy statements before adopting. Understanding these values will help you provide the best possible home for a rabbit.</p>
</div>
